OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FIf the planned changes to STV's news
OL,7,Fservice go through, the former Grampian
OL,8,Fregion will effectively become a
OL,9,Fsub-opt.
OL,11,FMore perceptive journalists and
OL,12,Fcommentators have noted that the
OL,13,Fboundary between STV's two services is
OL,14,Fdictated purely by transmitter coverage
OL,15,Fareas.
OL,17,FSo Fife is split between the two and
OL,18,Fthere are examples of towns and small
OL,19,Fcities which would arguably be better
OL,20,Foff in the other editorial area.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,200,140,120,200,0,100
