OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt is tempting to ask why the bulk of
OL,7,FScotland needed two separate ITV
OL,8,Flicences in the first place.
OL,10,FEver since it went on the air in 1957,
OL,11,FSTV has had a tendency to present
OL,12,Fitself as a Scottish national
OL,13,Fbroadcaster.
OL,15,FIts initial franchise area ` the
OL,16,Ffootprint of the Blackhill transmitter
OL,17,F` stretched from the Ayrshire coast to
OL,18,Fjust north of Dundee.
OL,20,FThis covered the vast bulk of the
OL,21,Fpopulation but a relatively small
OL,22,Fproportion of the landmass.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,200,140,120,200,0,100
