OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F159A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FInterestingly in 1960 the ITA proposed
OL,7,Fbuilding a transmitter between Perth
OL,8,Fand Dundee to improve reception there.
OL,9,FPresumably this would have been a relay
OL,10,Fof Blackhill. It was never built.
OL,12,FHowever by then the ITA had decided to
OL,13,Fgive a separate company, Grampian, the
OL,14,Ffranchise to broadcast on transmitters
OL,15,Fbeing built for Aberdeenshire and the
OL,16,Farea around Inverness.
OL,18,FThis was in line with the ITA policy to
OL,19,Ftry to increase the number of
OL,20,Fcompanies.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,200,140,120,200,0,100
