PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F159A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FFor the same reason Border and Westward
OL,7,Fcame on the air. There were legitimate
OL,8,Farguments that their transmitters could
OL,9,Fhave been allocated to neighbouring
OL,10,Festablished companies.
OL,12,FAnd this was one reason why the doomed
OL,13,FTeledu Cymru came into being too. It
OL,14,Fproved unviable for multiple reasons,
OL,15,Fpaving the way for a takeover by TWW
OL,16,Fand the West and Wales dual region
OL,17,Fwhich officially existed until a decade
OL,18,Fago.
OL,20,FGrampian was a different story.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,200,140,120,200,0,100
