OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FAfter a shaky start, it soon proved
OL,7,Fhugely popular in its heartland areas
OL,8,Fand was profitable.
OL,10,FGrampian was one of the ITA's golden
OL,11,Fboys. A much-loved local service
OL,12,Fperfectly in tune with its core
OL,13,Faudience.
OL,15,FSTV in the 60s was anything but the
OL,16,Fgolden boy.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,200,140,120,200,0,100
