PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F159A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FSome of its local output was personally
OL,7,Fderided by the ITA chairman Lord Hill.
OL,8,FAnd while hugely popular with the
OL,9,Fpublic, within creative circles in
OL,10,FScotland it was not uncommon to think
OL,11,FSTV could do much better.
OL,13,FIt would have been unthinkable in the
OL,14,F1967 franchise round for fundamental
OL,15,Fchanges which would simply have put
OL,16,FGrampian out of business. There was
OL,17,Fsimply no appetite for a franchise
OL,18,Fcovering central and northern Scotland.
OL,20,FInterestingly nobody competed against
OL,21,FGrampian for the licence.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,200,140,120,200,0,100
