OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FBy then, the Angus transmitter had
OL,7,Fturned Dundee and Perth from an STV
OL,8,Ffringe into a Grampian heartland.
OL,10,FBy 1980, STV had improved markedly even
OL,11,Fif it still had critics. Meanwhile
OL,12,FGrampian was seen as one of the most
OL,13,Fambitious of the small companies. So
OL,14,Fthe idea of merging the two licences
OL,15,Fnever came up.
OL,17,FThe 1991 auction was based on the
OL,18,Fexisting regional structure across the
OL,19,FUK.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,200,140,120,200,0,100
