CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F159A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt might be arguable that one company
OL,7,Fcovering all of Scotland ` including
OL,8,Fthe Border area ` could have been big
OL,9,Fenough to have had a stronger network
OL,10,Fpresence. It could have been required
OL,11,Fto provide separate local news and
OL,12,Fprogrammes for the north.
OL,14,FI do wonder though whether this might
OL,15,Fhave come to pass if STV in the 60s had
OL,16,Fbeen well thought of by the regulator.
OL,17,FA new Scottish broadcaster created by a
OL,18,Fmerger of the previous franchise
OL,19,Fholders. Afterall, the ITA came up with
OL,20,Fthis sort of solution for London.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,200,140,120,200,0,100
