OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut all this is history. For now, enjoy
OL,7,Fwhat will almost certainly be the final
OL,8,Fweeks of STV North.
OL,10,FOfcom's consultation on the proposals
OL,11,Fruns for another 3 weeks.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
